About 20y or so ago, the local craze was chocolate-covered coffee
beans.  Every male engineer had a bowl on his desk.  We all munched on
them throughout the day, drinking them down with coffee.  As time went
on and the frenzy level increased, we eventually caught on and the
contents were replaced.

